- Original Box: No





- Original Papers:No

- Model: DeVille

- Bracelet: Omega Leather Strap

- Dial: Saudi Stamped Tapestry Dial

Features:





- Rare Saudi Arabia Stamped Dial








Movement:





- Omega Quartz Movement

Warranty:

Shipping:

Seiko Coutura Solar Chronograph Radio-Sync Solar World Time 44.5mm Stainless Steel SSG009




World time technology meets fashion-forward design in this Coutura Radio-Sync Solar Chronograph watch from Seiko. Crafted in stainless steel, this quality timepiece features a 44.5mm case, black dial, LumiBrite hands, chronograph sub-dials, date display, blue accents, and second hand. Setting a new standard, the bezel displays 25 time zones. The stylish link bracelet secures with a deployment clasp. The accurate solar quartz movement takes its energy from light and stores it in a self-charging battery that never needs to be changed. Water-resistant to 100 metres, this wristwatch includes a three-year limited manufacturer's warranty. Radio Sync Solar World Time Chronograph technology offers the precision of one second every 100,000 years.




Radio Sync Solar Chronograph




Radio-controlled: Automatically receives radio signals to precisely adjust the time and calendar




Powered by light energy- no battery change required




Signal reception and result indicator




World time function (25 time zones)




24 hour indicator




6-month power reserve




Power save function




Chronograph measures up to 60 minutes in 1/5 second increments with split time measurement function




Date calendar




LumiBrite hands and markers




Screwdown crown




Glass caseback




Sapphire crystal




Case diameter: 44.5mm




Stainless steel case and bracelet




Cabochon crown




Water-resistant to 10 bar, 100 meters (330 feet)

Pre-Owned Jaeger-LeCoultre Master Compressor Diver GMT Navy Seals (Q178T470) self-winding automatic watch, features a 46mm titanium case surrounding a black dial on a black leather strap with a titanium tang buckle. Functions include hours, minutes, seconds, date, GMT and chronograph. 



Description


Jaeger LeCoultre Master Compressor Men's watch. Limited of 1500 Navy Seals edition. Titanium case with a black leather strap. Uni-directional rotating ceramic bezel. Black dial with luminous hands and stick hour markers. Arabic numeral marks the 12 o'clock position. Minute markers around the outer rim. Dial Type: Analog. Luminescent hands and markers. Date display between 4 and 5 o'clock positions. Chronograph - three sub-dials displaying: 60 second, 30 minute and 12 hour. Automatic movement. Calibre 757 engine. Scratch resistant sapphire crystal. Solid case back. Case diameter: 46 mm. Round case shape. Tang clasp. Water resistant at 300 meters/ 1000 feet. Functions: chronograph, date, hour, minute, second. Luxury watch style.
